### TEST 4: Social Media Search - POST /search
### Testing Social Media category with Reddit (no pagination support)
### ============================================================================

### 4.1 Basic social media search (category-based)
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "web development tips",
  "category": "social_media"
}

### 4.2 Search with Reddit bang (!re)
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "!re programming best practices"
}

### 4.3 Reddit search with specific engine parameter
POST http://localhost:8000/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "linux administration",
  "engine": "reddit"
}

